item.title: Exploding Into 80s action flix
item.description: Lock and load, geeks — this week we’re diving headfirst into the golden age of over-the-top explosions, muscle-bound heroes, and one-liners sharp enough to cut steel: the 1980s action movie era. From Arnold mowing down armies in Commando to Bruce Willis crawling through air vents in Die Hard, we’re talking the stars, the tropes, and the films that turned action into pure spectacle... item.title: Are You In Resonance Or Resistance? – Dr. Dolores Fazzino
item.description: The Dr. Dolores Show Have you ever noticed how some experiences feel effortless while others feel like pushing a boulder uphill? That inner tug-of-war is often a clue—are you in resonance or resistance? In this episode of The Dr. Dolores Show, we explore the energetic dynamics that either align you with your truth or pull you away from it.
